
This set of scripts as a simple wrapper around adapter and quality trimming functionality of MIRA and SGA assemblers.

Requirements:
MIRA assembler, https://sourceforge.net/projects/mira-assembler
SGA assembler, https://github.com/jts/sga

mira and sga executables should be in the PATH.

Usage: MIRA_CLIP.pl <libname>

should be run from the directry containing *.fastq.gz files to be processed.
